data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This magnificent home, overlooking the 15th Island Course of the World Renowned Innisbrook Golf, Spa and Tennis resort, Home to the Valspar Championship, is an exquisitely updated showcase. Upon entering the double front doors, one’s eyes quickly are trained on the fabulous in ground pool and golf course visible thru the living room’s hurricane rated accordion sliding doors, opening to the outdoor sitting area featuring a fireplace and TV. The Living Room with its fireplace provides a comfortable gathering area to catch up with friends. The living room and foyer both feature electronic chandelier caddies easing maintenance. The Dining Room features a beautiful chandelier and hidden uplighting providing the perfect atmosphere for elegant dining pleasure. Double doors off the living room lead to the first-floor office which incorporates dark wood built-ins. Modern elegance is how to define the Kitchen which features white and gray porcelain tile flooring, white quartz countertops, new expresso shaded, self-closing cabinets accent the stainless-steel appliances which include a dishwasher, SubZero refrigerator, 6 burner gas stove and double oven; wine refrigerator and convection microwave. Walk-in Pantry and separate Coffee bar add elegance for entertaining guests. Store your favorite bottles of vino behind glass encased temperature-controlled wine cellar conveniently located just off the Kitchen. Double doors from the Kitchen lead to your Entertainment wing featuring wood floors over a cork base for sound deadening; wall mounted TV with high end Atmos speakers w/AV equipment, back lite, cocktail bar. The Bar features an under-counter wine refrigerator and dishwasher. A full bath featuring a steam shower provides access directly from the entertainment room as well as access from the pool area.  The Owner Suite includes a double-sided fireplace, a sitting area with breathtaking views of the pool and golf course. Dual walk-in closets provide ample space. From the bedroom, feast your eyes upon your master bath which rivals those seen in magazines and showrooms. A soaking tub is the center piece of the room with a walk-in glass encased semi-circled rain shower at one end and dual vanities and cabinets on either side of the room. An additional Guest Bedroom with full bath provides a quiet getaway to accommodate guests or additional family members. A half bathroom off the kitchen and a large laundry room with ample cabinets and conveying washer and dryer completes the first level. Upstairs loft area includes a kitchenette, built-in desk and covered terrace overlooking the golf course. Two bedrooms each with their own full bathroom complete this level. Entertain guests with ease in the pool area which provides ample dining and sitting areas along with a new outdoor kitchen and bar. Heated and cooled, pebble tech, saltwater pool provides virtually year-round enjoyment. Other features include new water heater, (3) newer A/C units; Tesla charging station in A/C garage and natural gas generator. Resort membership offers 4 golf courses including the famed Copperhead course.  Other resort amenities include: 9 tennis courts, pickleball, Fitness Center, Spa, heated pools and several on-site restaurants.  Resort is minutes away from area attractions including Clearwater Beach, Dunedin, Pinellas Trail, Honeymoon Island, Caladesi Island Ferry, Tampa airport, Raymond James stadium and Amalie Arena.
